Version 0.11
  o new function frmode() to calculate the mode of a variable
  o new function histc() to fraw a histogram with an added distribution
    density curve
  o t.testAB() and anovaFK() have dedicated print methods
  o argument "new" from function dbinoms() is now FALSE by default
  o new argument "zoom" for function dbinoms(); if TRUE, the drawing only zooms
    on the values with a positive probability
  o new function hclr() pentru a genera culori din gama HCL (Hue Chroma Luminance)
  o function t.testAB() now also accepts a formula in the first argument
  o new function anovaFK() using the Fligner-Killeen test to verify the
    homogeneity of variance assumption
  o new function dfcalc() to calculate degrees of freedom
  o new function t.testAB() using the Ansari-Bradley test to verify the
    homogeneity of variance assumption
  o new function spooled() to calculate the pooled variance

Version 0.1
  o initial version
